# Cloudflare Pages redirects.
#
# Canonical host is the apex (xrpl-utilities.com). Forcing every www
# request to redirect to the apex keeps a single Origin for the entire
# site, so every .io backend's CORS allowlist only needs one entry and
# new services can ship without remembering to dual-allow www. The 301
# is permanent so browsers + search engines cache it and skip the hop
# on repeat visits.
#
# :splat preserves the path + query string verbatim so deep links still
# land on the right page after the host swap.
https://www.xrpl-utilities.com/*  https://xrpl-utilities.com/:splat  301!
